{"tid":2011481,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【暗黑兵法】用「好難食」取代「藍店不了」","createTime":"2020-05-11T04:41:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-11T06:20:10.000Z","uid":316947,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"56b7495b701bdabd8ac6b8672d25213da8a783b6","tid":2011481,"uid":316947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T04:41:02.000Z","msg":"眾所鳩知，我地推行黃色經濟圈其中一個環節係令到少啲人幫襯藍店<br />\n不過愈係留言藍店不了，就愈係有班藍絲支持<br />\n不如直接攻擊佢食物質素<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />等大家一諗起間店淨係諗到難食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「食飯唔好講政治<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />難食就係難食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我唔識政治嘢，我淨係知道好難食囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n「隔離嗰間嘢好食呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我理得佢係咪黃，好食就得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n所謂黃藍是政見，好食是良知<br />\n一齊幫藍店嘅食物質素唱通街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba2be38c7d5a9944cf1e41161f51dc7187c13a4d","tid":2011481,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T04:42:28.000Z","msg":"請求美國定性香港黑警為恐怖組織並執行香港人權及民主法案<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2011424\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2011424</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b7b3f1992b39f1045da50d059496b176c9553b0f","tid":2011481,"uid":192824,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T04:42:54.000Z","msg":"日日食，餐餐食<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">黃店</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"ca8cf7708763a3583d4cd01d5cfb52e610b2f1f3","tid":2011481,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T04:47:53.000Z","msg":"有老鼠"},{"pid":"5c4f7fccee9bf233d33bf84d475606f68fd56dac","tid":2011481,"uid":37389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11